Titolo: Everything (video game)

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: Everything is a simulation game developed by artist David OReilly. It was released for the PlayStation 4 on March 21, 2017, for Microsoft Windows and macOS on April 21, 2017, and for Linux on April 28, 2017. A Nintendo Switch version of the game was released on January 10, 2019. It was released in Japan on February 13, 2020. The game sees the player take control of various lifeforms and inanimate objects, exploring the procedurally generated world and finding new things to take control of. Everything features quotations from philosopher Alan Watts and has no clear goal aside from occupying more objects within the game. It received critical acclaim.

Genere: Simulation 

Valutazione: N/A
